Read the &quot;Manifesto against Labour&quot;
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=POHENPfWhi8" rel="nofollow">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=POHENPfWhi8</a>
<a href="http://www.krisis.org/1999/manifesto-against-labour" rel="nofollow">http://www.krisis.org/1999/manifesto-against-labour</a><p><i>Those who do not work (labour) shall not eat! This cynical principle is still in effect; all the more nowadays when it becomes hopelessly obsolete. It is really an absurdity: Never before the society was that much a labour society as it is now when labour itself is made superfluous.</i>
